n our side — as soon as the confirmation hits, the funds will appear in your balance.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\n\nPlease note that Rainbet has no control over blockchain speeds, as they depend entirely on network traffic and the cryptocurrency you’re using.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\n\nHere are the average confirmation times for popular coins:\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEthereum (ETH): Under 1 minute\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eRipple (XRP): Under 1 minute\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eBitcoin (BTC): Around 10 minutes\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLitecoin (LTC): Under 10 minutes\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSolana (SOL): Under 1 minute\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTron (TRX): Under 2 minutes\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eBNB (Binance Smart Chain): Under 2 minutes\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e","support_answer_3":"Cryptocurrency withdrawals on Rainbet are typically processed and sent within 5 minutes on average. This may vary slightly depending on platform traffic and network load at the time of your request.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\nOnce the withdrawal is sent, the time it takes to arrive in your wallet depends on the blockchain confirmation time and your wallet provider’s policies. Some wallets only credit funds after a specific number of confirmations.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\nHere’s an overview of typical confirmation speeds:\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEthereum (ETH): Under 1 minute\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eRipple (XRP): Under 1 minute\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eBitcoin (BTC): Around 10 minutes\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLitecoin (LTC): Under 10 minutes\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSolana (SOL): Under 1 minute\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTron (TRX): Under 2 minutes\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\